==English==

===Adjective===
'''agglutinate'''

# United with [[glue]] or as with glue; cemented together.
# Consisting of root words combined but not materially altered as to form or meaning; as, agglutinate forms, languages, etc.

===Verb===
'''agglutinate'''

# {{transitive}} To [[unite]], or cause to [[adhere]], as with glue or other viscous substance; to unite by causing an adhesion of substances.

===Related terms===
*[[agglutination]]

